        {
          "id": "977d8fb861d3_9",
          "href": null,
          "name": "a019",
          "text": "Yes, they were written to advertise my book and yet they also helped to almost double the visits to the Gaia Education website over the last couple of months. Please, join us in the effort of letting the world know about Gaia Education’s excellent work! Share your own story of learning or working with us, and in the process spread the word about Gaia Education. That too is design for multiple functions!",
