        {
          "id": "977d8fb861d3_10",
          "href": null,
          "name": "650e",
          "text": "[Note: from here on I am adding to the 2016 article.] I am republishing this year old article as the new edition of Gaia Education’s online programme in ‘Design for Sustainability’ (GEDS) is about to start in October. This programme was first created in 2008/9 as an online version of Gaia Education’s ‘Ecovillage Design Education’ 125 hour face-to-face programme and has evolved through a series of re-writes and expansions to a course that is almost an on-line masters for global-local (glocal) change agents.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
