          "href": null,
          "name": "3f70",
          "text": "For anyone wanting to be part of the transition to diverse regenerative cultures everywhere, the GEDS (enrolling now!) is a great place to start by getting inspired by a whole systems design approach to redesigning the human impact on Earth from by and large exploitative and destructive to predominantly collaborative and regenerative.",
