          "id": "977d8fb861d3_14",
          "href": null,
          "name": "42f9",
          "text": "Personally, I feel deeply grateful for having had the opportunity to share much of the research I did for my 2006 PhD in ‘Design for Human Planetary Health’ and my 2016 book ‘Designing Regenerative Cultures’ with the students on Gaia Education’s excellent online and face-to-face programmes. May it serve!",
